<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>yé sū chì zé fēng hé hǎi 迦南980</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 yé sū chì zé fēng hé hǎi, yī qiè dōu píng jìng.
 shén de ér nǚ ya, nǐ yào gāng qiáng, yé sū yǐ dé shèng.
 tóng shēng qí dǎo, tóng shēng chuī jiǎo, tóng xīn jǐng xǐng.
 zhǔ dìng yì yào fù xìng cǐ de, mó guǐ yǐ zhàn jīng.
 kàn nǎ wǔ gǔ yǐ fā shēng, xiāng bǎi mǎn shān lǐng.
 shén de bǎi xìng dōu yào yī tóng zì jié, róng yào guī zhǔ míng.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>980</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>